tool_description: This api can be used to build league tournament fixtures, knockout tournament fixtures, combination grouping tournament fixtures and for tournament table creation
name: Sport Api
title: Sport Api

api_list.name: retrieve league tournament fixtures for a team
api_list.description: This request is used to retrieve already created league tournament fixtures for a team.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sport-api6.p.rapidapi.com/api/leagues/fixtures/cac42164-f34c-4c08-8861-9f43caafe4fd/villareal"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sport-api6.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://sport-api6.p.rapidapi.com/api/leagues/fixtures/{uid}/{team_name}"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sport-api6.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
